  <div class="row">
     <div class="col-md-6">
       <p class="gray-text">Guidelines for Contact information</p>
       <ul class= "closed-to-view ">
         <li>We recommend that athletes set up an email address specifically for recruiting.</li>
         <li>You may also want to consider the say for a contact phone.</li>
         <li>Remember that the email address and phone number used as contact information will be seen by a large number of coaches.</li>
       </ul>
     </div>
